e psyche's; intent captured belongs to her as a distinct psyche with her own intent layer. *natural language processing*] Low Minimum Zero [])) (2v57 ([(Technology (Software (Data Formats)))] Clarification [The square-bracket string idea is not meant as schema-dependent delimiter reuse: the psyche is reasoning that a string is conceptually a vector of characters, analogous to capitalized True and False exposing bool as an enum-like concept.] Low Minimum Zero [])) (4vi4 ([(Technology (Software (Distributed EventDrivenArchitecture)))] Clarification [Nexus can have a daemon internal interface distinct from external Signal and SEMA surfaces. Inside Nexus there may be a recursive computation engine that can call back into itself and provide a future runtime control substrate for prioritizing actor work handling busy SEMA capacity preserving logging and deciding when to tell clients the system is too busy.] Low Minimum Zero [])) (5g4d ([(Technology (Software (Intelligence AgentSystems)))] Clarification [For supervised browser-agent work, the preferred browser surface is the human's main Chrome profile rather than a temporary guest automation profile, so logged-in state and familiar browser context are available when safe.] Low Minimum Zero [])) (5grv ([(Technology (Software Data))] Principle [Spirit needs topic catalog queries *query processing*] Low Minimum Zero [])) (699n ([(Technology (Software Intelligence))] Clarification [Spirit search may grow beyond simple filters toward weighted keyword or recency scoring, potentially using the Nexus language for richer query logic; this is exploratory direction rather than a settled immediate production requirement. *information retrieval*] Low Minimum Zero [])) (6zci ([(Technology (Software (Intelligence AgentSystems)))] Principle [Persona Pi is the Codex advisor harness for Persona] Low Minimum Zero [])) (750r ([(Technology (Software (Intelligence AgentSystems)))] Decision [Spirit's intent gate should use a strong open-weight 